此反应可看作是[[Mannich反应|Mannich反应]]的烷基硼酸变体。它提供了除[[还原胺化反应|还原胺化反应]]以外一种合成取代胺类的方法。

==应用==
利用[[发散合成法|发散合成法]]制备多官能团产物：<ref>{{cite journal en| author = Naoya Kumagai, Giovanni Muncipinto, Stuart L. Schreiber | journal = [[Angewandte_Chemie_International_Edition|Angewandte Chemie International Edition]] | year = 2006 | volume = 45 | pages = 3635–3638 | doi = 10.1002/anie.200600497 | title = Short Synthesis of Skeletally and Stereochemically Diverse Small Molecules by Coupling Petasis Condensation Reactions to Cyclization Reactions}}</ref> <ref>反应物：L-苯基乳酸、丙酮、L-苯基丙氨酸甲酯和一个烷基硼酸。反应在乙醇中室温下进行，非对映体过量百分数99％。</ref>

